     <pre><code>helm upgrade --install=true --wait=true --timeout=10m0s &nbsp;--debug --namespace=ef-external --values=external/bitnami/mongodb/values-ha.yaml mongo&nbsp; external/bitnami/mongodb/
</code></pre>
