  <h3 id="id-(4.3)GeographicalDeploymentofExpertflowCXwithRedundancy-DeployingStatefulComponents"><span id="GeographicalDeploymentofExpertflowCXwithRedundancy-DeployingStatefulComponents"></span>Deploying Stateful Components&nbsp;
   <i18n-message i18nkey="clipboard.copyLink.label" attribute="description">
    <copy-clipboard class="anchor-copy-button" value="https://docs.expertflow.com/cx/4.3/geographical-deployment-of-expertflow-cx-with-redu#id-(4.3)GeographicalDeploymentofExpertflowCXwithRedundancy-DeployingStatefulComponents">
