     </svg>
    </copy-clipboard>
   </i18n-message></h3>
  <p>To circumvent ActiveMQ's availability we have provided it with cloud replicated storage to keep it's storage in, this solves the high availability challenge. We will be using cstor that we deployed above to provide cloud replicated storage. And updating it's connection strings if not already updated. Below is the list of changes made to it's deployment yaml containing the changes.</p>
